    "description": "<p>Estabilished in 2023 and growing business with passionate team members lead by Er Cavan Chai.</p>\n<p>The collective strength of CVC is built on the diverse skills in various Civil and<br>\nStructural &nbsp;disciplines. &nbsp;We &nbsp;collaborate &nbsp;extensively &nbsp;with &nbsp;professionals &nbsp;from<br>\ndifferent &nbsp;fields, &nbsp;including &nbsp;architects, &nbsp;Mechanical, &nbsp;Electrical, &nbsp;Geotehnical &nbsp;<br>\nProfessional &nbsp;Engineers &nbsp;(PE), &nbsp;and &nbsp;Registered &nbsp;Surveyors, &nbsp;to &nbsp;offer &nbsp;integrated<br>\nsolutions. &nbsp;CVC's &nbsp;team &nbsp;holds &nbsp;several &nbsp;prestigious &nbsp;certifications, &nbsp;including<br>\nQualified &nbsp;Erosion &nbsp;Control &nbsp;Professional &nbsp;(QECP), &nbsp;Structural &nbsp;Engineer &nbsp;(SE) &nbsp;for<br>\nStructural &nbsp;Inspections, &nbsp;Competent &nbsp;Person &nbsp;(CP) &nbsp;for &nbsp;Facade &nbsp;Inspections, &nbsp;and<br>\nDesign for Safety Professional (DfSP).</p>",
